      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:5",
      "text": "：Leif Pedersen",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:7",
      "text": "：Attach to RenderMan lights（连接到 RenderMan lights）",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:8",
      "text": "Overview（资源概览）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:9",
      "text": "这是一个面向 RenderMan 的 production-ready lights library，包含 19 个 IES profiles。",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:10",
      "text": "IES profiles 可以帮助你获得 physical photometric data distribution。换句话说，它会基于原始 manufacturer specifications 提供 realistic light emission pattern，为你的 art 增添更多 realism。",
      "ascii_letters": 111,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:14",
      "text": "这个 IES lights library 包含以下 IES profiles ...",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:16",
      "text": "要安装到 RenderMan 的 Preset Browser 中，请将",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:18",
      "text": "folder 放入你的 RenderMan Asset Library 的",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:19",
      "text": "LightRigs",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:20",
      "text": "folder。建议将安装默认的 RenderManAssetLibrary folder 转移到非安装目录中、且具有 full writing privileges 的位置。",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:21",
      "text": "当你转移 Materials folder 并把 Asset Library 移到其他位置后，必须通过 Maya preferences 告诉 Maya 使用新的 path。",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:22",
      "text": "或者，你可以像这样在 Maya.env file 中创建新的 environment variable：",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "7736e8cef0:25",
      "text": "Public Domain. Free of known copyright restrictions.（公有领域，无已知版权限制。）",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    }
  ],
